{"lemma":"قِصَّةُ","slug":"قِصَّةُ","root":"ق.ص.ص","root_slug":"ق-ص-ص","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ص-ص","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":9},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n35689","n35699","n35700","n35701"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D9%90%D8%B5%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"story, tale, relation"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"petition"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plot"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"synopsis"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pudendum"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"event"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"affair"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"case"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"gypsum"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/qisˤ.sˤa/","/qasˤ.sˤa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n35689","headword_ar":"قَصَّهُ","root":"qS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, A, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~N","text_ar":"قَصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he clipped it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shore it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cut off from it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K;) namely, hair, (S, M, A, K,) and wool, (M,) and plumage, (A,) and a nail of a finger or toe; (M, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miqaS~","text_ar":"مِقَصّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.: (A, K:) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qS~Shu","text_ar":"قصّصهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, A,) and, by permutation,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~aAhu","text_ar":"قَصَّاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M:) or these two forms have an intensive signification: or you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlZ~ufora wanaHowahu","text_ar":"الظُّفْرَ وَنَحْوَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~ayotu","text_ar":"قَصَّيْتُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I pared the nail and the like."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b2-  Also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a weaver)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cut off from it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a garment, or piece of cloth,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its unwoven end,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extremity, consisting of warp without woof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut off the extremities of his ears."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, M.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quS~iyhi","text_ar":"قُصِّيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurs in a trad., as meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Take thou from the extremities of his ears."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [But this may be from the root"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qSw","text_ar":"قصو"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.] ―         -b4-  And [hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~a A@ll~`hu xaTaAyaAhu","text_ar":"قَصَّ ا@للّٰهُ خَطَايَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God diminished,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deducted from,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the account of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his sins."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, from a trad.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~a A^avarahu","text_ar":"قَصَّ اَثَرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, A, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSaSN","text_ar":"قَصَصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, A, O, L, K,) in [some of] the copies of the K"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSiySN","text_ar":"قَصِيصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but the former is the right, (TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~N","text_ar":"قَصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He followed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"followed after, his track,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"footsteps, in pursuit; endeavoured to trace him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"track him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, Msb, K, &c.;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he did so by degrees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at any time:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA:) which last is the correct explanation: (TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~ahu","text_ar":"قَصَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same, (A, TA,) and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Avrh","text_ar":"اثره"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AqtS~","text_ar":"اقتصّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Avrh","text_ar":"اثره"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tqS~S","text_ar":"تقصّص","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, M, K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qas~a","text_ar":"قَسَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a dial. form of the same. (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraja fulaAnN","text_ar":"خَرَجَ فُلَانٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSaSFA fiY A^avari fulaAnK","text_ar":"قَصَصًا فِى اَثَرِ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one went forth following,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"following after, the footsteps of such a one, in pursuit."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And it is said in the Kur, [xviii. 63,] (S,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA@rotad~aA EalaY A=vaArihimaA qaSaSFA","text_ar":"فَا@رْتَدَّا عَلَى ا=ثَارِهِمَا قَصَصًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And they both returned by the way by which they had come, retracing their footsteps."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b2-  [And hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~a Ealayohi Alxabara","text_ar":"قَصَّ عَلَيْهِ الخَبَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, * K, *) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHadiyva","text_ar":"الحَدِيثَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~uw^oyaA","text_ar":"الرُّوْيَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSaSN","text_ar":"قَصَصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, TA,) or this is a subst. put in the place of the inf. n. so that it has become predominant over it, (S,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~N","text_ar":"قَصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, TA,) or the latter only is the inf. n., and the former is [only] a subst., (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He related to him the piece of news,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"information,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the tradition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"story,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the dream,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in its proper manner"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY wajohihi","text_ar":"عَلَى وَجْهِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"): (S, Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made it known"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHadiyva","text_ar":"الحَدِيثَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AqtS~","text_ar":"اقتصّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he related the tradition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"story, in its proper manner"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY wajohihi","text_ar":"عَلَى وَجْهِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"); (S, K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as though he followed its traces, in pursuit, and related it accordingly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he pursued the course of the tradition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"story:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxabara","text_ar":"الخَبَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tqS~S","text_ar":"تقصّص","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he pursued,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sought after, the particulars of the news,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"information, gradually, and deliberately."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~a","text_ar":"قَصَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also said to signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He recited,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"delivered, a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"discourse such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuTobap","text_ar":"خُطْبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) And it is said in the Kur, [xii. 3,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHonu naquS~u","text_ar":"نَحْنُ نَقُصُّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayoka A^aHosana AlqaSaSi","text_ar":"عَلَيْكَ اَحْسَنَ القَصَصِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We explain unto thee with the best explanation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~N","text_ar":"قَصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the inf. n. of the verb used in this sense, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSaSN","text_ar":"قَصَصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a subst. [syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiS~apN","text_ar":"قِصَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]. (TA.) And in a trad. respecting the Children of Israel it is said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lam~aA qaS~uwA halakuwA","text_ar":"لَمَّا قَصُّوا هَلَكُوا"},{"kind":"text","text":": or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lam~aA halakuwA qaS~uwA","text_ar":"لَمَّا هَلَكُوا قَصُّوا"},{"kind":"text","text":": accord. to different relations: meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"When they relied upon words,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and neglected works,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they perished:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when they perished,"},{"kind":"text","text":"by neglecting works,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they inclined to, and relied upon, stories."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~ahu Almawotu","text_ar":"قَصَّهُ المَوْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~ahu EalaY Almawoti","text_ar":"قَصَّهُ عَلَى المَوْتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina Almawoti","text_ar":"مِنَ المَوْتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 4."}],"source_refs":["S","M","A","Msb","K","TA","O","L","T"]},{"entry_id":"n35699","headword_ar":"قَصَّةٌ","root":"qS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~N","text_ar":"قَصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last signification; the latter in three places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n35700","headword_ar":"قُصَّةٌ","root":"qS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hair over the forehead;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naASiyapN","text_ar":"نَاصِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, A,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEaru Aln~aASiyapi","text_ar":"شَعَرُ النَّاصِيَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) accord. to some, (TA,) of a horse: (M, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what comes forward, thereof, over the face:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA:) and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nASyp","text_ar":"ناصية"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a woman: (M:) or the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tur~ap","text_ar":"طُرَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e., the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nASyp","text_ar":"ناصية"},{"kind":"text","text":", [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"front hair of the head,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is cut over"},{"kind":"text","text":"(lit. over against,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hi*aA='a","text_ar":"حِذَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the forehead:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what a woman makes, in the fore part of her head, by cutting the hair of that part, excepting over her temples:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or it signifies, as some say, (Mgh,) or signifies also, (M, A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any lock of hair:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, A, Mgh:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quSaSN","text_ar":"قُصَصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiSaASN","text_ar":"قِصَاصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, K) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quSaASN","text_ar":"قُصَاصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"kind":"page_break","n":2528}],"source_refs":["M","A","TA","Mgh","Msb","K"]},{"entry_id":"n35701","headword_ar":"قِصَّةٌ","root":"qS","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A story; a narrative:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is written:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an affair;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a case:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSaSN","text_ar":"قَصَصٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is syn. therewith, in the first of the above senses; (S, * M, A, * Msb, * TA;) and signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a story,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"narrative, related:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSiySapN","text_ar":"قَصِيصَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"also is syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiS~apN","text_ar":"قِصَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the first of the above senses], (A, K,) and so is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSiySN","text_ar":"قَصِيصٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiS~apN","text_ar":"قِصَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiSaSN","text_ar":"قِصَصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqaA SiySu","text_ar":"اَقَا صِيصُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a pl. pl.: (A, * TA:) and the pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSiySapN","text_ar":"قَصِيصَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSaAy^iSu","text_ar":"قَصَايِصُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A, * TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu qiS~apN EajiybapN","text_ar":"لَهُ قِصَّةٌ عَجِيبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSaSN","text_ar":"قَصَصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He has,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, relates, a wonderful story"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY raA^osihi qiS~apN","text_ar":"فِى رَاْسِهِ قِصَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In his head is a speech;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA qiS~atuka","text_ar":"مَا قِصَّتُكَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is thine affair?"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thy case?"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rafaEa qiS~apF A_ilaY","text_ar":"رَفَعَ قِصَّةً اـِلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~uloTaAni","text_ar":"السُّلْطَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He referred an affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a case, to the Sultán"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~N","text_ar":"قَصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last signification."}],"source_refs":["S","M","TA","K","Msb","A"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}